# iLO targets: one per line. Optional username and password per line (else use -u and -p).
#
# Format (space-separated):
#   IP                    -> use -u and -p
#   IP password           -> use -u, this password
#   IP username password  -> use this username and password
#
# Format (comma-separated):
#   IP,password
#   IP,username,password
#
# Examples (uncomment and edit):
# 192.168.1.10
# 192.168.1.11 mypassword
# 192.168.1.12 admin adminpass
# 192.168.1.13,secret
# 192.168.1.14,iloadmin,secret
